<lb n="1"/><note n="68-1">Each line begins with the symbol O</note>śubhamastu <g type="danda">.</g> penugoṁḍe virapaṁṇayyanavara Anumatiyiṁda
<lb n="2"/>cauṭakūra basavaṇasōmayājigaḷū virapaṁṇayya
<lb n="3"/>navara bāgila sēnabōva gōraṁṭiya tiṁmappanū barasida
<lb n="4"/>I lakhkhaṇāpurada mahālakṣmidēvaṁmmanavara I śilāśāsa
<lb n="5"/>nagaḷige maṁgaḷa mahā śrīśrīśrī
